title: Daana Veera Soora Karna
writer: Taraka Rama Rao Nandamuri, Taraka Rama Rao Nandamuri
actors: Taraka Rama Rao Nandamuri, Dhulipala, Mikkilineni, Harikrishna Nandamuri, Prabhakar Reddy, Satyanarayana Kaikala, Varalakshmi S., Saroja Devi B., Prabha, Sharada, Kanchana, Nandamuri Balakrishna, Unni Mary, Jaya Bhaskar, Chalapathi Rao
description: Abandoned at birth, brave and loyal Karna grows up to acquire skills as a warrior to battle the Pandavas.
